data.description: Welcome to Skybrook!  Original owner's pride shows in this well maintained townhouse.  Spacious open floor plan features main level great room w/ceiling fan & gas log FP, dining area, eat in kitchen w/granite countertops, tile backsplash, 2 pantries and recent S/S appliances. Plus a flex space the opens to covered deck. Upper level offers primary suite w/trey ceiling/fan, WIC, garden tub/separate shower and dual sinks.  Also, 2 additional spacious bedrooms, guest bath and laundry.  Lower level is where you enter the home from garage.  4th bedroom/den w/ceiling fan, WIC, full bath, and storage space complete this level w/covered patio access.  This is a must see townhouse in Cabarrus County!
